snippet.title: Amber Heard Makeup Tutorial - Allure December 2017 Cover | makeupbymolliw
snippet.description:
Hey loves!  I hope you enjoy this recreation of Amber's look!

PRODUCTS MENTIONED:
-Too Faced Primed and Poreless Primer
-Lancome Teint Idole Ultra Cushion Foundation in "310 Bisque C"
-Maybelline Fit Me Foundation in "110 Porcelain"
-Urban Decay Naked Skin Concealer in "Light/Neutral"
-Studio Makeup Loose Setting Powder
-Makeup Forever Fond De Teint Powder Foundation in "200"
-Sugarpill Eyeshadow in "Buttercupcake"
-Morphe X Jaclyn Hill Palette in "Creamsicle", and "Mocha" 
-Benfiet Gimme Brow in "5"
-Sonia Kushuk Lipliner in "True Red"
-Smashbox Lipstick in "Bing"
-Dirty Little Secrets Liquid Lipstick in "Phantom"
-Best Damn Beauty Setting Spray
-The Makeup Eraser AmpliMascara


FOLLOW ME:
-Instagram is @makeupbymolliw
